{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/HighresScreenshot04.png?t=1728562321\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A?</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your main goal is to escape from the so-called, surreal and confusing, &quot;<strong>Klobgniak's Home</strong>&quot; and if possible, solve Klobgniak's mystery and find his hideout. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/ScreenShot02.png?t=1728562321\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MAKING NOISE</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try not to make noise and be well hidden. <strong>Walking</strong>, <strong>running</strong>, <strong>jumping</strong> and other <strong>interactions with the environment</strong> can be heard, so wait for the right moment to act.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In several rooms there are small &quot;<strong>homes</strong>&quot; where you can hide. While you're hidden here you cannot be spotted or &quot;<strong>Returned</strong>&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/ScreenShot03.png?t=1728562321\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RETURNED</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every time you're <strong>Returned</strong>, you'll have to start over and all the progress you've made will be lost. When that happens, some <strong>items</strong> that will be important for you to make progress could be <strong>hidden in different, random locations and places</strong>, and sometimes, some kind of <strong>tool</strong> will be needed to get to them.\u00a0If you are caught with some <strong>Klobgniak's items</strong>, you will be <strong>punished</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/NEWScreenshotStorePage__27_.png?t=1728562321\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PUNISHMENT</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Rebels and thieves must be punished.&quot;</strong> While you are punished, your movement is restricted. You are required to <strong>pay</strong> to remove the punishment.\u00a0However, you could escape without paying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Good luck! </strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/20efc8a2cb0ce9a3c124268a93ad9c5f76dab4df.jpg"},{"name":"The Saint","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/62966fed89a51e95254cfe8da5304440ecc7b7a6.jpg"},{"name":"Returned","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/331ea3985cedfe7661adf55725650689fad16c10.jpg"},{"name":"Unconscious Mind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/da25356a59a5a74d20a8e5332e92ee3d926065d7.jpg"},{"name":"The Musician","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/e873fe02ce31043ead003d426102c0fb44a766d0.jpg"},{"name":"The Culprit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/c33e6c0a3079aec5fc1b4dc086ff65a4e09a7a8c.jpg"},{"name":"Education?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/ef6a0d7d17114d12394e7bf91ce500287e31becc.jpg"},{"name":"Generosity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3122270/2d20163ed37d0ddbc9484037eaf98af433372ee5.jpg"},{"name":"Follow the Light","path":"https://cdn.